reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Anker USB C Charger Cable [2 Pack, 6ft] - Consistent Quality and Performance
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Anker USB C Charger Cable set, which includes two 6ft, 310 Type C Charger Cables, and I must say, these cables are yet another testament to Anker's reputation for quality and reliability. These cables have not only met but exceeded my expectations, solidifying my trust in Anker products.The length of the cables (6ft each) is one of their most convenient features. This extra length offers much-needed flexibility and ease of use, allowing me to charge my devices comfortably even when the power outlet is not in immediate proximity. This is especially useful in scenarios like airports, coffee shops, or even just lounging on the couch.Fast charging capability is a standout feature of these cables. They efficiently power up my devices in significantly less time compared to standard cables. This is a major advantage for anyone who relies on quick charging to keep their devices up and running throughout a busy day.Durability is another key aspect of these cables. The braided design not only gives them a premium feel but also adds to their strength and longevity. They are resistant to the usual wear and tear that comes from regular use, tangling, and bending, making them a long-lasting investment.The build quality is impressive, with sturdy connectors that fit snugly and securely into devices. This snug fit ensures a stable connection for charging, reducing the risk of disconnection or damage to the charging port.In terms of compatibility, these Anker cables work flawlessly with a wide range of USB-C devices. This versatility is a huge plus, as it means I can use the same cables for multiple devices, reducing the need for carrying different types of cables.In conclusion, the Anker USB C Charger Cable set is a superb purchase for anyone in need of reliable, fast-charging, and durable cables. Anker continues to impress with their commitment to quality, and these cables are no exception. They are a worthwhile addition to my collection of tech accessories, and I highly recommend them to others looking for top-quality charging cables.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Robust and Reliable, An Ideal Cable Solution!
reviews.reviewText: The Anker USB C Cable pack is a testament to quality and reliability. Right from the first touch, the durability of these cables is evident. They feel well-built and sturdy, ready to withstand the rigors of daily use.The 3ft length hits the sweet spot, offering ample reach while avoiding the clutter that longer cables can sometimes create. It's a practical length for everyday use, whether connecting devices on a desk or charging a phone while on a couch.The performance of these cables is as impressive as their build quality. The connectivity is seamless, ensuring fast and efficient charging and data transfer. I have faced no issues with connection drops or slow charging, which is a relief.The inclusion of two cables in the pack amplifies the value for the price, making this purchase a smart and economical choice. It's always handy to have an extra cable for the car, office, or any other place you might need to charge or connect your devices.In a market flooded with cables that can be hit or miss, the Anker USB C Cable stands out as a dependable choice. The quality that Anker has brought to the table with these cables is commendable. They have become a trustworthy companion for my devices, delivering consistent performance without burning a hole in the pocket.For anyone in need of reliable USB C cables that offer good length, durability, and excellent performance without breaking the bank, this pack from Anker is definitely worth considering. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great deal, great cables.
reviews.reviewText: They are what they are supposed to be. Nothing flashy or extra about them. They work great and that's all you need them to do.

I have purchased many charging cables over the years before realizing that both the cable and block both need to be good quality to get a fast charge on the newer devices. These work great, I am always worried about purchasing longer cables. They are durable enough to keep in a vehicle and put up with the abuse.

reviews.reviewTitle: Great USB cable works with CarPlay on an iPhone 15 Pro
reviews.reviewText: These cables are great quality with the braided sheath, and very flexible. I have USB-A ports in my car, so I needed an A to C cable to use CarPlay with my iPhone 15 Pro, and it works perfectly.

reviews.reviewTitle: Excelente cable para carga de dispositivos que soporten conexión USB-C
reviews.reviewText: Los compré para cargar mis Galaxy Buds Live y una tablet, y hasta ahora han funcionado bastante bien. El material les da buena resistencia y la longitud es ideal para no tener que estar cerca del cargador de pared. La velocidad de transferencia que detecté fue de 480 Mbps, básicamente la de un USB-2. Los recomiendo ampliamente.
